         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl"><hi>Tarmasene</hi> [the <hi>Pañcwarike</hi>] ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// [On the 11th day], ... for the <hi>saṃgha</hi> ... ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// On the 13th day, one spoonful. ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">On the [15th] day, one [spoonful]. ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl"><hi>Puñarakṣite</hi> the <hi>Pañcwarike</hi> has seen. ¤ ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a6"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:ching2010"/><citedRange>379</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[On the 16th day], the oil/ghee for the <hi>saṃgha</hi> has been spent: one (spoonful). ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a7"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// one spoonful. ... ///</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
